titles.short: The Very Sleepy Tille/Personal Space
titles.full: The Very Sleepy Tille/Personal Space

summaries.short: Esme and Roy try to get a sleepy Tillie to take a nap and encourage Hugo and Frank to include baby Fig in their big kid game.
summaries.full: It’s time for Tillie to take a nap -- but she wants to play with Esme and Roy instead. How will the Monster Sitters get a sleepy Tillie to rest so she can be her best? When baby Fig is left out of Hugo and Frank’s space explorer game, Esme and Roy encourage the big kids to include her!
